snippet.title: BOLERO - Elvish Yadav & Manisha Rani | Preetinder | Asees Kaur | Rajat Nagpal | Babbu | Anshul Garg
snippet.description:
Anshul Garg presents Bolero featuring Elvish Yadav & Manisha Rani 

Audio credits :-
Singer : Preetinder & Asees Kaur
Composer : Preetinder
Lyrics : Babbu
Music : Rajat Nagpal

Video credits :-
Featuring Elvish Yadav & Manisha Rani 
Director : Nitish Raizada
DOP : Sukh Kamboj  
Editor DI & Colorist  : Ismile 
Assistant Directors : Kevin Thakur 
Line Producer : R.S Films and production Production Assistant- Jadu, Rohit, Honey, Gogi & Aamir
Costume Stylist : Rajat Manchanda
Hairstylist : Salman
Still Photography : Akki
Art Director : Pinky Art 
Jimmy Gib : Gourav
Choreographer : Smile masih

PlayDMF Team:-
Founder & CEO : Anshul Garg
PlayDMF Project Head : Raghav Sharma 
PlayDMF Project Manager : Sankalp Garg
Artist Manager : Gaurav Arora
PlayDMF Team : Ashima Chauhan & Akshay Mahadik
Artwork : Vicky Sandhu
Special Thanks : Ingrooves Team 

https://www.ingrooves.com/

Ingrooves Team :-
Head : Amit Sharma 
Team : Nagesh Jadhav, Kajal Israni, Amol Suryavanshi, Lavanya Das & Nishtha Sikroria

Travel and hospitality partner :- PRM Hospitality

Lyrics :-
Tumse pyar kahan hoga tum to faraar ho jaate ho*
4 gaadiyan aati hain kalli ko milne aate ho*
Logon ke jo haath jurhaate
Aake baithte pairon mein
Choti choti baatein hoti
Rehti hain bade shehron mein
Tu baith ton sahi bolero mein

Tu poori hai meri aur adha gurgaon apna hai
10 saal pehle karndiya jo ab logon k sapna hai
Raaton ko to sune the fire hote hain*
Dopehron mein*
Choti choti baatein hoti
Rehti hain bade shehron mein
Tu baith ton sahi bolero mein

Minister lagte ho babbu itna na tamjham karo*
Dar lagta hai duniya se ab itna bhi na naam karo*
Minister lagte ho elvish itna na tamjham karo*
Dar lagta hai duniya se ab itna bhi na naam karo*
Bas abhi to charche hote hain
Kuch apno mein kuch gairon mein
Choti choti baatein hoti
Rehti hain bade shehron mein
Tu baith ton sahi bolero mein

About YRF Spy Universe:
YRF Spy Universe is a first of its kind cinematic universe of spy thriller films in India. The first film in the universe, "Ek Tha Tiger," starring Salman Khan and Katrina Kaif was released in 2012, followed by its sequel "Tiger Zinda Hai" in 2017. The third film in the universe, "War," was released in 2019 and starred Hrithik Roshan and Tiger Shroff in pivotal roles. The recent release Pathaan (2023) starring Shah Rukh Khan, Deepika Padukone and John Abraham is the fourth instalment in the spy universe franchise.

All the films of the Spy Universe are blockbusters with Pathaan being the all-time highest grossing Hindi film ever. The YRF Spy Universe is now one of the biggest IP’s in the history of Indian cinema. The next film from this franchise is Tiger 3 releasing this Diwali!

YRF Spy Universe films boast of incredible visual spectacles with high-octane action sequences, thrilling plot-lines, power-packed characters and musical chartbusters.

Episode 75: The Happy Couple
 -----------------------------------------------------------------
Reyansh's father arrives in Dehradun and tells the Khanna family about Reyansh's truth. Malini and Viren gets shocked after knowing the truth. Meanwhile, Kriti reveals her plan in front of Jai. Will the engagement ceremony go smoothly? or any major twist waiting for Aradhana? What will happen now? Watch the episode to learn more. 

Show Name: Barsatein - Mausam Pyaar Ka

Episode: 75
Director: Atif Khan
Producer: Ekta Kapoor

#barsateinmausampyaarka #setindia #बरसातेंमौसमप्यारका #kushaltandon #shivangijoshi 

About Barsatein - Mausam Pyaar Kaa:
------------------------------------------------------------
A sensible and ambitious journalist joins a media company run by a suave maverick man. While united in their passion for honest and ground-breaking journalism, their contrasting characters immediately put them at loggerheads. What will happen when she starts falling in love with him despite the red flags? 'Barsatein - Mausam Pyaar Ka' stars Shivangi Joshi and Kushal Tandon in lead roles.

About YRF Spy Universe:
YRF Spy Universe is a first of its kind cinematic universe of spy thriller films in India. The first film in the universe, "Ek Tha Tiger," starring Salman Khan and Katrina Kaif was released in 2012, followed by its sequel "Tiger Zinda Hai" in 2017. The third film in the universe, "War," was released in 2019 and starred Hrithik Roshan and Tiger Shroff in pivotal roles. The recent release Pathaan (2023) starring Shah Rukh Khan, Deepika Padukone and John Abraham is the fourth instalment in the spy universe franchise.

All the films of the Spy Universe are blockbusters with Pathaan being the all-time highest grossing Hindi film ever. The YRF Spy Universe is now one of the biggest IP’s in the history of Indian cinema. The next film from this franchise is Tiger 3 releasing this Diwali!

YRF Spy Universe films boast of incredible visual spectacles with high-octane action sequences, thrilling plot-lines, power-packed characters and musical chartbusters.

snippet.title: TVF Aspirants - Season 2 | Official Trailer | Streaming from 25 Oct On Amazon Prime Video
snippet.description:
Get ready for the highly anticipated return of Aspirants as they continue to take us on a rollercoaster ride of friendship, dreams, and dilemmas. As we witness the mentorship dynamic between Sandeep Bhaiya and Abhilash evolve, we're left with questions about how they'll manage their professional responsibilities alongside their deep friendship. 

From Rajinder Nagar to Rampur, this season takes our aspirants into the world of adulthood, testing their decisions in the face of life's challenges. Drama, laughter, and a whirlwind of emotions await you in this season.

#AspirantsOnPrime , new season 25th October!

Recap Aspirants Season 1 here: https://youtube.com/playlist?list=PLTB0eCoUXErY_KvRNKOERQtYSDPjOb8jw&si=TaG8xWK8ZrQEEjFD

A TVF Creation
Director: Apoorv Singh Karki
Writers: Deepesh Sumitra Jagdish, Ashutosh Chaturvedi, Pankaj Mavchi
Producer: Arunabh Kumar
Executive Producers: Vijay Koshy, Shreyansh Pandey
Cast: Naveen Kasturia, Sunny Hinduja, Abhilash Thapliyal, Shivankit Parihar, Namita Dubey

hi.title: TVF Aspirants - Season 2 | Official Trailer | 25 अक्टूबर से Amazon Prime Video पर
hi.description:
एस्पिरेंट्स की बहुप्रतीक्षित वापसी के लिए तैयार हो जाइए क्योंकि ये हमें दोस्ती, सपनों और दुविधाओं की रोलरकोस्टर सवारी पर ले जायेंगे। जैसे-जैसे हम संदीप भैया और अभिलाष के बीच मार्गदर्शन के रिश्ते को विकसित होते देखते हैं, हमारे पास यह सवाल रह जाता है कि वे अपनी गहरी दोस्ती के साथ-साथ अपनी पेशेवर जिम्मेदारियों को कैसे संभालेंगे।

राजिंदर नगर से रामपुर तक, यह सीज़न हमारे एस्पिरेंट्स को वयस्कता की दुनिया में ले जाता है, जीवन की चुनौतियों के सामने उनके निर्णयों का परीक्षण करता है। इस सीज़न में ड्रामा, हंसी और भावनाओं का बवंडर आपका इंतजार कर रहा है।

snippet.title: Aspirants Season 2 - Official Trailer | Prime Video India
snippet.description:
Prime Video Presents 
Aspirants Season 2 - Official Trailer
Directed by Apoorv Singh Karki
Starring Naveen Kasturia, Sunny Hinduja, Shivankit Singh Parihar, Abhilash Thapliyal, Namita Dubey

Rajinder Nagar to Rampur, the next journey of our Aspirants begin 🫰🏻
#AspirantsOnPrime , new season 25th October!

About:
It is the story of the journey of three UPSC Aspirants and their friendship against all odds.

About Prime Video: Prime Video is a premium streaming service that offers Prime members a collection of award-winning Amazon Original series, thousands of movies & TV shows—all with the ease of finding what they love to watch in one place. Prime Video is just one of the many benefits of a Prime membership, available for just ₹1499/ year. 
Included with Prime Video: Thousands of acclaimed TV shows & movies across languages & geographies, including Indian films such as Shershaah, Soorarai Pottru, Sardar Udham, Gehraiyaan, Jai Bhim, Jalsa, Shakuntala Devi, Sherni, Narappa, Sarpatta Parambarai, Kuruthi, Joji, Malik, and HOME, along with Indian-produced Amazon Original series like Farzi, Jubilee, Dahaad, The Family Man, Mirzapur, Made in Heaven, Four More Shots Please!, Mumbai Diaries 26/11, Suzhal – The Vortex, Modern Love, Paatal Lok, Bandish Bandits, Guilty Minds, Cinema Marte Dum Tak, and Amazon Original movies like Maja Ma & Ammu. Also included are popular global Amazon Originals like Citadel, The Lord of The Rings: The Rings of Power, Reacher, Tom Clancy's Jack Ryan, The Boys, Hunters, Fleabag, The Marvelous Mrs. Maisel, & many more, available for unlimited streaming as part of a Prime membership. Prime Video includes content across Hindi, Marathi, Gujarati, Tamil, Telugu, Kannada, Malayalam, Punjabi, & Bengali. 
Prime Video Mobile Edition: Consumers can also enjoy Prime Video’s exclusive content library with Prime Video Mobile Edition at ₹599 per year. This single-user, mobile-only annual video plan offers everyone access to high-quality entertainment exclusively on their mobile devices. Users can sign-up for this plan via the Prime Video app (on Android) or website. 
Instant Access: Prime Members can watch anywhere, anytime on the Prime Video app for smart TVs, mobile devices, Fire TV, Fire TV stick, Fire tablets, Apple TV, & multiple gaming devices. Prime Video is also available to consumers through Airtel and Vodafone pre-paid & post-paid subscription plans. In the Prime Video app, Prime members can download episodes on their mobile devices & tablets & watch anywhere offline at no additional cost.
Enhanced experiences: Make the most of every viewing with 4K Ultra HD- & High Dynamic Range (HDR)-compatible content. Go behind the scenes of your favourite movies & TV shows with exclusive X-Ray access, powered by IMDb. Save it for later with select mobile downloads for offline viewing. 
Video Entertainment Marketplace: In addition to a Prime Video subscription, customers can also purchase add-on subscriptions to other streaming services, as well as, get rental access to movies on Prime Video. Prime Video Channels: Prime Video Channels offers friction-free & convenient access to a wide range of premium content from multiple video streaming services all available at a single destination – Prime Video website & apps. Prime Members can buy add-on subscriptions & enjoy a hassle-free entertainment experience, simplified discovery, frictionless payments, & more. Rent: Consumers can enjoy even more movies from new releases to classic favourites, available to rent – no Prime membership required. View titles available by visiting primevideo.com/store. The rental destination can be accessed via the STORE tab on primevideo.com & the Prime Video app on Android smart phones, smart-TVs, connected STBs, & Fire TV stick.

snippet.title: SSC | EP 02: मुखर्जी नगर | Amit Bhadana
snippet.description:
Watch Episode 01- https://youtu.be/AlAJ3Ykst7E?si=ph-KCKhEg5qwpuur

Download Adda247 App:  https://adda247.app.link/Amit_Bhadana_E2

Adda247, India's largest vernacular Exam preparation company founded in 2010. Adda247 provides well curated course content & teaching by top faculties of industry for all types of Exam preparations, i.e., Govt jobs, IIT, Medical, State Exams, etc.

Rate Us On IMDB: https://www.imdb.com/title/tt29424187/

Kisi bhi ladai mein insaan ki aadhi jeet tabhi ho jati hai jab vo ladne ki himmat juta le. Student Shiv ko uske papa ne ghar se nikaal diya hai aur ab vo aa gaya hai Mukherjee Nagar ke warzone mein, jahan sapne bante bhi hai aur bigadte bhi. Dosari taraf SSC sir ke best teacher ko Khanna hijack kar leta hai aur us par ilzaam bhi lagata hai. Nayi nayi problems sar utha rahi hain lekin hope ki ungali thame Shiv aur SSC badh rahe hain kadam dar kadam.

snippet.title: Meri Jaan / Ya Tuli Khanjar Maare | Bhoomi 2023 | Mithoon | Abdul Rashid Hafiz, Asees Kaur | Kashmir
snippet.description:
We're back with a beautiful Sufi Hindi and Kashmiri song - #MeriJaan by #Mithoon and #AbdulRashidHafiz. It's a powerful expression of separation and talks about love in a very unique way with a very impactful sound. The Hindi part is written by A M Turaz and the Kashmiri composition is written by Abdul Ahad Nazim.

#MeriJaan is the fourth song from GoDaddy India presents #Bhoomi2023, powered by Moha 

Subscribe to our channel for more music everyday 🔔 

To SUBSCRIBE click the link below:
http://www.youtube.com/subscription_center?add_user=SalimSulaimanMusic

Lyrics - 

Cheshma wuchh wuchh chaayni wayn mye gaah soryom, donn achhan 
Myenkin wayn saarnyee, cheshma baadaam aysitan

Mere jeene ka saara..
Hmm.. Mere jeene ka saara..
Mere jeena ka saara samaan lete jao
Mera chaen-o-sukoon mera
Itminan lete jao

Jo ja rahe ho jaana x3
Meri jaan lete jao 

Mere jeena ka saara samaan lete jao
Mera chaen-o-sukoon mera
Itminan lete jao

Jo ja rahe ho jaana x3
Meri jaan lete jao 

Yim Zaar Vanhas Bardar
Kar Sanaa Su Yaar Bozey

Ya Tuli Khanjar Maarey
Nat Saayn Shabaa Rozey 

Iss ishq mein had tak jaan-e-talak ki
saari wafaye meri hai
Ki tumhara ismein kuch bhi nahi
saari khataye meri x3

Dil khol ke mujhko tum..
Dil khol ke mujhko tum Ilzaam dete jao

Jo ja rahe ho jaana x3
Meri jaan lete jao 

Maashok Kyah Goi Keenai 
Aatash Mye Bortham Seenai

Aashak Chhu Kaym Taam Deenai
Maaroony Ravaa Rozey

Yim Zaar ..

Mere jeena ka saara
Aatash Mye Bortham Seenai x2
Mere jeena ka saara
Aashak Chhu Kaym Taam Deenai
Maaroony Ravaa Rozey
Mere jeena ka saara samaan lete jao

snippet.description:

खुसखुशीत कडाकणी | कडकणी मऊ व तेलकट न होण्यासाठी या 2 चुका टाळा | कुरकुरीत कडकणी Navratri Kadakani
कडाकणी 
कडाकणी रेसिपी | नवरात्र स्पेशल रेसिपी | दसरा सणानिमित्त खास रेसिपी  | सप्तमी खास कडाकणी माळ रेसिपी | खुसखुशीत व कुरकुरीत कडाकणी रेसिपी | पारंपरिक रेसिपी |  महाराष्ट्रीयन कडाकणी रेसिपी | कडाकणी रेसिपी मराठी | गोड पुरी रेसिपी | kadakani Recipe | Navratra Special Recipe | Sapatami Special Mal Recipe | Dasara Special Recipe | Crispy and Crunchy Kadakani Recipe | Tradational Recipe | Maharashtrian Kadakani Recipe | Kadakani REcipe Marathi | Sweet Puri Recipe | 
साहित्य | Ingredients 
 • मैदा २ कप | Maida 2 cup 
 • बारीक रवा १/२ कप | Fine Semolina ½ cup 
 • पिठी साखर ३/४ कप | Sugar Powder ¾ cup  
 • दूध ३/४ कप | Milk ½ cup 
 • मीठ २ चिमूट | Salt 2 pinch 
 • तेल २ मोठे चमचे | Oil 3 tbsp 
 • तेल तळण्यासाठी  | Oil for frying 
Kadakani Recipe 
 • First add milk and sugar together. Let sugar melt. 
 • In a parat take semolina, maida and salt together and mix.
 • Now add oil mohan to the maida.
 • Mix well. 
 • Knead tight dough with using sugar milk. Cover and keep for 2 hours. 
 • Roll to make thin layer kadakani and fry this till it gets light golden colour.   
Other Recipes

snippet.title: Tu Jaana Na Piya | Official Music Video | New Life | KING
snippet.description:
#TuJaanaNaPiya #KING #NEWLIFE

‘Tu Jaana Na Piya’ is the romantic magnum opus on ‘NEW LIFE’ which is set to win hearts across the globe. Offering another look into his vulnerable side, KING lays his heart bare on this raw, emotive record while portraying various shades of being lovestruck and melancholy.

Tere aake yun, jaane se
Baichain hai fiza meri
Ho har nazar, har khabar
Pe rehti nigah meri
Ho tujhe kaise ye batayein humne kya kya dekha
Kaise logo se rishte the, kaise the mere karam
Hum kahi kho na jaaye ye darr hai rehta
Tu haath thaam ke mera bas todh de bharam
Soona saa ye jahaan
Kaali raaton mein hum
Tanha baithe ye yahaan
Tujhse ek hi cheez maangte hain hum
Tu jaana na piya
Mera tere bina koi na yaha
ye dil keh raha

Tu jaana na piya
Chhoti si umar se sab hai dekha
ab jhela jaye na
Tu Aaja…

par baatein kayi na chhup saki

Chora Baba Ka

Fortuner dholi rakhi

Langot band koli rakhi

Ram bole sab se tera

Baba aage jholi rakhi

Sanjho te sada dhola le re

Modhe pe bhola le re

Khet mein se gola bn rya

Naya udhan khatola le re

Dur te dhamak sune gaadiya k base ka

Photo chapvaya piche shankara k face ka

Naam chal va rha jo vilata mein bhi desh ka

Chora Baba Ka

Chora Baba Ka


Yo Khon ghana tata rave

Rees kare mari uka jee bada khata rave

Kabje mein saata rave

LV k dufla mein laal hara paata rave

Paira mein Gucci body pe fendy

Bhai tera fashiona mein trendy

Naare te na g

Gaddiya mein enzy

Daab k clip kare empty

Seat niche magnum rakhe

Lagte na toll na hi roke mane naake

Chori kade dekhiya tu maine ajmake

Tere ghare ake tane leyaunga byah ke

Chora Baba Ka

Chora Baba Ka

Chora Baba Ka

Chora Baba Ka

Gaadi uchi chodhe rim gaddi sue 100 pe

Daffa kafi dafa lagi hai giroh pe

Sochi khuti pe juti tutti bole re

Mere yaar is area ki toop hai

Chora jamma desi hai bhai

Moda pe khesi hai bhai

Milna to haj ajaiyo

Kal toh mahri peshi hai bhai

Ik Load automode karu magazine khali

Mere lath taiyaar je na goli chali

Sheeshe down tera town hungame mein

4 yaar hai faraar gurdgame mein

Oh Up k asli hai Chambal ki goli hai

Finance ki gaddi mein yaara ki tooli hai

Kon k keh rha hai chrd raftaar

Yaar duniya hai duniya toh B* hai

Ghut maar hoke ki Cha pi tu dhabe ki  

Tension na liyo bhai khon kharabe ki  

Haryana baithe hai  

Bombay mein nai ae

Ohra system bitha denge  

Jai babe ki

Chora Baba Ka

snippet.title: NEW! Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah | Ep 3906 | 19 Oct 2023 | Teaser
snippet.description:
Click here to subscribe to SAB: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

Episode 3906: Vicky Ka Cheque
--------------------------------------------------------
Jetha is thrilled to thank Babita for assisting him in obtaining Vicky's order. Taarak warns him not to get too enthusiastic until he receives money for the order. Jetha is confident and presents Vicky's cheque since he is hopeful about the deal. Jetha phones Nattu Kaka to drop the cheque off at the bank, but Nattu Kaka tells him that things may be delayed due to Navaratri. Jetha is disappointed when he hears this. Nattu Kaka then informs Vicky that her paycheck is due in 10 days. What is Jetha going to do now?

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episodes No - 3906, 19 Oct 2023
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sab #Latest #New #TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah2023 #tmkocfunnyepisodes #hindicomedy #comedyvideo #15yearsoftmkoc  

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

Click here to watch the episode of Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah :

snippet.description:
Damini tells Meethi that Ichha committed a crime to save Kanha's life and that she doesn't consider Ichha to be a criminal. Damini tells Meethi to be proud of Ichha. Meethi denies to forgive Ichha.

Meethi नहीं माफ़ कर सकती Ichha को | Uttaran | उतरन | Full Episode | Ep. 909


--------
📺 Welcome to the captivating world of 'Uttaran' on Colors TV! 🎬

🤝 Join us on this roller-coaster journey of friendship, love, and betrayal as we delve into the lives of two extraordinary friends from starkly contrasting backgrounds.

👸 Meet Tapasya, the pampered and privileged daughter of a wealthy man, and her best friend, Ichcha, who comes from a humble background as the daughter of a maid. Despite society's barriers, their unbreakable bond challenges conventions and stands the test of time.

💔 Love takes center stage when Veer, whose marriage proposal was rejected by Tapasya, finds solace in the companionship of Ichcha. But what ensues is a whirlwind of emotions as jealousy and heartbreak threaten to tear apart the inseparable duo.

💍 Witness a gripping twist when Tapasya, fueled by spite, takes a drastic step and marries Veer, setting off a chain of events that creates a complex love triangle. Veer finds himself torn between the two friends, entangled in a web of emotions.

🔄 Spanning over thousands of episodes, 'Uttaran' takes you on an emotional roller-coaster, exploring the lives of these characters, their triumphs, their struggles, and the undeniable fate that intertwines their destinies.

👨‍👩‍👧‍👦 As the story unfolds, follow the lives of their children and witness how the choices made by their parents continue to shape their future, testing their bonds and unraveling new mysteries.

🔥 Brace yourself for a gripping tale of love, loyalty, and sacrifice that will keep you on the edge of your seats, episode after episode.

📺 Welcome to the captivating world of 'Uttaran' on Colors TV! 🎬

🤝 Join us on this roller-coaster journey of friendship, love, and betrayal as we delve into the lives of two extraordinary friends from starkly contrasting backgrounds.

👸 Meet Tapasya, the pampered and privileged daughter of a wealthy man, and her best friend, Ichcha, who comes from a humble background as the daughter of a maid. Despite society's barriers, their unbreakable bond challenges conventions and stands the test of time.

💔 Love takes center stage when Veer, whose marriage proposal was rejected by Tapasya, finds solace in the companionship of Ichcha. But what ensues is a whirlwind of emotions as jealousy and heartbreak threaten to tear apart the inseparable duo.

💍 Witness a gripping twist when Tapasya, fueled by spite, takes a drastic step and marries Veer, setting off a chain of events that creates a complex love triangle. Veer finds himself torn between the two friends, entangled in a web of emotions.

🔄 Spanning over thousands of episodes, 'Uttaran' takes you on an emotional roller-coaster, exploring the lives of these characters, their triumphs, their struggles, and the undeniable fate that intertwines their destinies.

👨‍👩‍👧‍👦 As the story unfolds, follow the lives of their children and witness how the choices made by their parents continue to shape their future, testing their bonds and unraveling new mysteries.

🔥 Brace yourself for a gripping tale of love, loyalty, and sacrifice that will keep you on the edge of your seats, episode after episode.

Credits:
Title: Jai Ambe Gauri Aarti
Singer: Alka Yagnik
Music Director: Navin-Manish
Edit & Gfx : Prem Graphics PG
Label: Music Nova

Lyrics:
जय अम्बे गौरी मैया जय श्यामा गौरी
Jai Ambe Gauri Maiya Jai Shyama Gauri
तुमको निशदिन ध्यावत
Tumko Nishadin Dhyavat
हरि ब्रह्मा शिवरी
Hari Bramha Shivari
ॐ जय अम्बे गौरी
Om Jai Ambe Gauri

मांग सिंदूर विराजत टीको मृगमद को
Mang Sindur Virajat, Tiko Mrigamad Ko
मैया टीको मृगमद को
Maiya Tiko Mrigamad Ko
उज्ज्वल से दो नैना उज्ज्वल से दो नैना
Ujjval Se Do Naina Ujjval Se Do Naina
चंद्रवदन नीको
Chandravadan Niko
ॐ जय अम्बे गौरी
Om Jai Ambe Gauri

कनक समान कलेवर रक्ताम्बर राजै
Kanak Saman Kalevar, Raktambar Raje
मैया रक्ताम्बर राजै
Maiya Raktambar Raje
रक्तपुष्प गल माला रक्तपुष्प गल माला
Raktpushp Gal Mala, Raktpushp Gal Mala
कण्ठन पर साजै
Kanthan Par Saje
ॐ जय अम्बे गौरी
Om Jai Ambe Gauri

केहरि वाहन राजत खड्ग खप्परधारी
Kehari Vahan Rajat, Khadag Khappar Dhari,
मैया खड्ग खप्परधारी
Maiyan Khadag Khappar Dhari
सुर नर मुनि जन सेवत सुर नर मुनि जन सेवत
Sur-Nar-Munijan Sevat Sur-Nar-Munijan Sevat
तिनके दुखहारी
Tinake Dukhahari
ॐ जय अम्बे गौरी
Om Jai Ambe Gauri

कानन कुण्डल शोभित नासाग्रे मोती
Kaanan Kundal Shobhit, Nasagre Moti,
मैया नासाग्रे मोती
Maiya Nasagre Moti
कोटिक चन्द्र दिवाकर कोटिक चन्द्र दिवाकर
Kotik Chandra Divakar Kotik Chandra Divakar
राजत सम ज्योति
Rajat Sam Jyoti
ॐ जय अम्बे गौरी
Om Jai Ambe Gauri

शुम्भ-निशुम्भ बिदारे महिषासुर घाती
Shumbh-Nishumbh Bidare Mahishasur Ghati
मैया महिषासुर घाती
Maiya Mahishasur Ghati,
धूम्र विलोचन नैना धूम्र विलोचन नैना
Dhumr Vilochan Naina Dhumr Vilochan Naina
निशिदिन मदमाती
Nishadin Madamati
ॐ जय अम्बे गौरी
Om Jai Ambe Gauri

चण्ड-मुण्ड संहारे, शोणित बीज हरे
Chand-Mund Sanhare, Shonit Bij Hare
मैया शोणित बीज हरे
Maiya Shonit Bij Hare
मधु-कैटभ दो‌उ मारे मधु-कैटभ दो‌उ मारे
Madhu-Kaitabh Dou Mare Madhu-Kaitabh Dou Mare
सुर भयहीन करे
Sur Bhayahin Kare
ॐ जय अम्बे गौरी
Om Jai Ambe Gauri

ब्रहमाणी रुद्राणी तुम कमला रानी,
Bramhani, Rudrani, Tum Kamala Rani,
मैया तुम कमला रानी
Maiya Tum Kamala Rani
आगम-निगम बखानी आगम-निगम बखानी
Agam Nigam Bakhani Agam Nigam Bakhani
तुम शिव पटरानी
Tum Shiv Patarani
ॐ जय अम्बे गौरी
Om Jai Ambe Gauri

चौंसठ योगिनी गावत, नृत्य करत भैरव
Chausath Yogini Gavat, Nritya Karat Bhairu
नृत्य करत भैरव
Nritya Karat Bhairu
बाजत ताल मृदंगा, बाजत ताल मृदंगा
Bajat Tal Mridanga, Bajat Tal Mridanga
और बाजत डमरु
Aru Baajat Damaru
ॐ जय अम्बे गौरी
Om Jai Ambe Gauri

तुम ही जग की माता, तुम ही हो भरता
Tum Hi Jag Ki Mata, Tum Hi Ho Bharata
मैया तुम ही हो भरता
Maiya Tum Hi Ho Bharata
भक्‍तन की दु:ख हरता भक्‍तन की दु:ख हरता
Bhaktan Ki Dukh Harta Bhaktan Ki Dukh Harta
सुख सम्पत्ति करता
Sukh Sampati Karta
ॐ जय अम्बे गौरी
Om Jai Ambe Gauri

भुजा चार अति शोभित, वर-मुद्रा धारी
Bhuja Char Ati Shobhi, Varamudra Dhari
मैया वर-मुद्रा धारी
Maiya Varamudra Dhari
मनवान्छित फल पावत मनवान्छित फल पावत
Manvanchhit Fal Pavat Manvanchhit Fal Pavat
सेवत नर-नारी
Sevat Nar Nari
ॐ जय अम्बे गौरी
Om Jai Ambe Gauri

कन्चन थाल विराजत, अगर कपूर बाती
Kanchan Thal Virajat, Agar Kapur Bati
मैया अगर कपूर बाती
Maiya Agar Kapur Bati
श्रीमालकेतु में राजत, श्रीमालकेतु में राजत
Shrimalaketu Mein Rajat Shrimalaketu Mein Rajat
कोटि रतन ज्योति
Koti Ratan Jyoti
ॐ जय अम्बे गौरी
Om Jai Ambe Gauri

श्री अम्बेजी की आरती जो को‌ई नर गावै
Shri Ambe Ji Ki Aarti Jo Koi Nar Gave
कहत शिवानन्द स्वामी कहत शिवानन्द स्वामी
Kahat Shivanand Swami Kahat Shivanand Swami
सुख सम्पत्ति पावै
Sukh-Sampatti Pave
ॐ जय अम्बे गौरी
Om Jai Ambe Gauri

जय अम्बे गौरी मैया जय श्यामा गौरी
Jai Ambe Gauri, Maiya Jai Shyama Gauri
तुमको निशदिन ध्यावत
Tumko Nishadin Dhyavat
हरि ब्रह्मा शिवरी
Hari Bramha Shivari
ॐ जय अम्बे गौरी
Om Jai Ambe Gauri

कनक समान कलेवर रक्ताम्बर राजै
Kanak Saman Kalevar, Raktambar Raje
मैया रक्ताम्बर राजै
Maiya Raktambar Raje
रक्तपुष्प गल माला रक्तपुष्प गल माला
Raktpushp Gal Mala, Raktpushp Gal Mala
कण्ठन पर साजै
Kanthan Par Saje
ॐ जय अम्बे गौरी
Om Jai Ambe Gauri

केहरि वाहन राजत खड्ग खप्परधारी
Kehari Vahan Rajat, Khadag Khappar Dhari,
मैया खड्ग खप्परधारी
Maiyan Khadag Khappar Dhari
सुर नर मुनि जन सेवत सुर नर मुनि जन सेवत
Sur-Nar-Munijan Sevat Sur-Nar-Munijan Sevat
तिनके दुखहारी
Tinake Dukhahari
ॐ जय अम्बे गौरी
Om Jai Ambe Gauri

कानन कुण्डल शोभित नासाग्रे मोती
Kaanan Kundal Shobhit, Nasagre Moti,
मैया नासाग्रे मोती
Maiya Nasagre Moti
कोटिक चन्द्र दिवाकर कोटिक चन्द्र दिवाकर
Kotik Chandra Divakar Kotik Chandra Divakar
राजत सम ज्योति
Rajat Sam Jyoti
ॐ जय अम्बे गौरी
Om Jai Ambe Gauri

शुम्भ-निशुम्भ बिदारे महिषासुर घाती
Shumbh-Nishumbh Bidare Mahishasur Ghati
मैया महिषासुर घाती
Maiya Mahishasur Ghati,
धूम्र विलोचन नैना धूम्र विलोचन नैना
Dhumr Vilochan Naina Dhumr Vilochan Naina
निशिदिन मदमाती
Nishadin Madamati
ॐ जय अम्बे गौरी
Om Jai Ambe Gauri

चण्ड-मुण्ड संहारे, शोणित बीज हरे
Chand-Mund Sanhare, Shonit Bij Hare
मैया शोणित बीज हरे
Maiya Shonit Bij Hare
मधु-कैटभ दो‌उ मारे मधु-कैटभ दो‌उ मारे
Madhu-Kaitabh Dou Mare Madhu-Kaitabh Dou Mare
सुर भयहीन करे
Sur Bhayahin Kare
ॐ जय अम्बे गौरी
Om Jai Ambe Gauri

ब्रहमाणी रुद्राणी तुम कमला रानी,
Bramhani, Rudrani, Tum Kamala Rani,
मैया तुम कमला रानी
Maiya Tum Kamala Rani
आगम-निगम बखानी आगम-निगम बखानी
Agam Nigam Bakhani Agam Nigam Bakhani
तुम शिव पटरानी
Tum Shiv Patarani
ॐ जय अम्बे गौरी
Om Jai Ambe Gauri

चौंसठ योगिनी गावत, नृत्य करत भैरव
Chausath Yogini Gavat, Nritya Karat Bhairu
नृत्य करत भैरव
Nritya Karat Bhairu
बाजत ताल मृदंगा, बाजत ताल मृदंगा
Bajat Tal Mridanga, Bajat Tal Mridanga
और बाजत डमरु
Aru Baajat Damaru
ॐ जय अम्बे गौरी
Om Jai Ambe Gauri

तुम ही जग की माता, तुम ही हो भरता
Tum Hi Jag Ki Mata, Tum Hi Ho Bharata
मैया तुम ही हो भरता
Maiya Tum Hi Ho Bharata
भक्‍तन की दु:ख हरता भक्‍तन की दु:ख हरता
Bhaktan Ki Dukh Harta Bhaktan Ki Dukh Harta
सुख सम्पत्ति करता
Sukh Sampati Karta
ॐ जय अम्बे गौरी
Om Jai Ambe Gauri

भुजा चार अति शोभित, वर-मुद्रा धारी
Bhuja Char Ati Shobhi, Varamudra Dhari
मैया वर-मुद्रा धारी
Maiya Varamudra Dhari
मनवान्छित फल पावत मनवान्छित फल पावत
Manvanchhit Fal Pavat Manvanchhit Fal Pavat
सेवत नर-नारी
Sevat Nar Nari
ॐ जय अम्बे गौरी
Om Jai Ambe Gauri

कन्चन थाल विराजत, अगर कपूर बाती
Kanchan Thal Virajat, Agar Kapur Bati
मैया अगर कपूर बाती
Maiya Agar Kapur Bati
श्रीमालकेतु में राजत, श्रीमालकेतु में राजत
Shrimalaketu Mein Rajat Shrimalaketu Mein Rajat
कोटि रतन ज्योति
Koti Ratan Jyoti
ॐ जय अम्बे गौरी
Om Jai Ambe Gauri

श्री अम्बेजी की आरती जो को‌ई नर गावै
Shri Ambe Ji Ki Aarti Jo Koi Nar Gave
कहत शिवानन्द स्वामी कहत शिवानन्द स्वामी
Kahat Shivanand Swami Kahat Shivanand Swami
सुख सम्पत्ति पावै
Sukh-Sampatti Pave
ॐ जय अम्बे गौरी
Om Jai Ambe Gauri

जय अम्बे गौरी मैया जय श्यामा गौरी
Jai Ambe Gauri, Maiya Jai Shyama Gauri
तुमको निशदिन ध्यावत
Tumko Nishadin Dhyavat
हरि ब्रह्मा शिवरी
Hari Bramha Shivari
ॐ जय अम्बे गौरी
Om Jai Ambe Gauri

snippet.title: Every Indian Mom | Ft. Tena Jaiin | The Paayal Jain
snippet.description:
Hey Guys ,
This video shows different behavious of Every Indian Mom . This is a very comic and relatable video . Mom packing birthday gift for neighbour 's child . Packing birthday gift and giving multiple instructions to behave properly in family gatherings with relatives . 90's style cake , samosa , dhokla chips . Indian Mom always convincing daughter to get married and not to be too choosy for the right guy for being husband . Boys , sundays and cricket matches . Chintu on the early sunday morning trying to sneakout to play bat ball with his friends . Savitri being the strict mom , took him to sabzi mandi . Navratri and durga maa pooja , navratri Fast food , Navratri vrat khana , bhabhi making everything for nanad and beti feeding them with hindu fast food , sabudana , kuttu , makhana , aloo , samak and avoiding onion , garlic Fasting all 9 days then preparing for kanjak . Guests coming suddendly with Ramleela Vip passes watching ram sita hanuman and excitment of going to dussehra mela ravan . Moms bragging about how modern they are and they give so much freedom to their kids , on the contrary daughter is having flashbacks of how her mom so strict . Mom waking childern on sunday despite everyone's holiday , she works all the days of the week cooking fresh breakfast , aloo ke parathe , watching them eat makes her happy and she sacrifices her own food for the love of her child . Moms when gives threat to leave the house , goes sit in the stairs , then in mandir , whole indian family goes out searching for maa , daughter crying for mom , she comes back . Maa Vs beti . Maa Beti during school picnic , school holiday homework . school exams , those exam days hiding answer sheets from her , moms during holi ,  Indian parents about privacy and using facebook , instagram social media , comparing their kids with other topper kids , not ever satisfied with their excellence , warning daughter about sex when she enters her college life , daughter and her first period , freaking out on periods , over feeding beti and then blaming her for being over weight bubbly child and not letting do dieting , surprising mom on her birthday with gift and cake mother gets shocked and scolds her for wasting money , never happy , Mothers and their millions of excuses when it comes to exercising or changing life. Mummy shouting , gossiping, watching serials and many more crazy situations. Still our mothers love us and we love our mother so much
Relish and Relive your Childhood Memories.. You will have major nostalgia

snippet.title: Ghost | Second OGM | Dr.Shivarajkumar | Anupam Kher | Jayaram | Prashant Narayanan | Sandesh | Srini
snippet.description:
This action packed heist thriller, directed by Srini, tells the story of one man's quest for justice. This apart the film offers a link to the second installment of "Birbal Trilogy", the director's awaited legal thriller. Powerhouse talents such as Dr Shivarajkumar, Anupam Kher, Jayaram, Prashanth Narayan, Archana Jois, Satyaprakash and Dattanna are part of the film's main cast.
Arjun Jaya's striking background scores and cinematographer Mahendra Simha's captivating visuals promise to take the film a notch higher.
We now welcome you to the world of #GHOST. See you in the cinemas this Dasara.

snippet.title: NEW! Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah | Ep 3905 | 18 Oct 2023 | Teaser
snippet.description:
Click here to subscribe to SAB: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

Episode 3905: Babita Bani Mediator
--------------------------------------------------------
Jetha is taken aback when she discovers that Vicky is Babita's friend's spouse. Vicky and Jetha had a dispute at his shop not long ago, and Vicky refused to place his order. Babita attempts to reconcile them and urges that they overcome their differences. Jetha, as always, respectfully listens to Babita and converses with Vicky. Vicly also apologizes for being impolite. Vicky also orders from the Gada shop. Jetha treats Bagha and Nattu Kaka to Kesar faluda to celebrate the success of such a large order. Later, Vicky returns to the Gada shop and expresses gratitude by wearing similar-looking outfits to Jetha.

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episodes No - 3905, 18 Oct 2023
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sab #Latest #New #TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah2023 #tmkocfunnyepisodes #hindicomedy #comedyvideo #15yearsoftmkoc  

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

Napoleon is a spectacle-filled action epic that details the checkered rise and fall of the iconic French Emperor Napoleon Bonaparte, played by Oscar®-winner Joaquin Phoenix. Against a stunning backdrop of large-scale filmmaking orchestrated by legendary director Ridley Scott, the film captures Bonaparte's relentless journey to power through the prism of his addictive, volatile relationship with his one true love, Josephine, showcasing his visionary military and political tactics against some of the most dynamic practical battle sequences ever filmed.

Directed by: Ridley Scott

Written by: David Scarpa

snippet.title: पतिला उठाकर Bhide की निकली हवा | Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah | Comedy Lagataar
snippet.description:
Click here to subscribe to Sony SAB Channel:
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

Sodhi and Roshan surprise Gogi early in the morning by coming to Jethalal's house. Now, stay tuned to know what Gogi's reaction will be after seeing his parents and whether he will be willing to go back to his house and stay with his parents.

Show Name - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast - Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi, Neela Asit Modi
Episode - 1153

#taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sab 

About The Show:
----------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a comedy show inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada Family which consists of uneducated businessmen Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal’s Wife Daya & their naughty Son Tipendra Gada living in 'Gokuldham Co-operative Society' and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. In case of a problem and emergency, Jethalal Gada often rushes to Taarak Mehta to seek his help and guidance, as he finds a philosopher in him. The housing society residents help each other find solutions when facing common, real-life challenges and getting involved in sticky situations.

Click here to watch the 'Comedy Lagataar' episodes from Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PL6Rtnh6YJK7ZAg6W-3De1ssi64wfuZyw6

►*About*
-------------
RadhaKrishn ke shaashwat prem ke vishay mein to sabhi ko gyaat hai. Radha bina Krishn nahin aur Krishn bina nahin Radha! Yadi Krishn Hriday hain, to Radha us hriday ki gati. Is premi yugal ki is mahagaatha mein aap jaanenge ki kis tarah Radha aur Krishn ne apne prem ko sansaar mein sthaapit kiya aur samast sansaar ko prem ki paribhasha sikhaayi, kyonki prem to bahut se log karte hain kintu keval prem ko paane ke liye… parantu RadhaKrishn ka prem ek-doosre ko paane ke liye nahin, apitu sansaar ko prem sikhaane ke liye tha. To dekhte rahiye RadhaKrishn ki ye anokhi prem-gaatha, jo Krishn nahin, apitu Radha ki drishti se likhee gayi hai!

📺 Welcome to the captivating world of 'Uttaran' on Colors TV! 🎬

🤝 Join us on this roller-coaster journey of friendship, love, and betrayal as we delve into the lives of two extraordinary friends from starkly contrasting backgrounds.

👸 Meet Tapasya, the pampered and privileged daughter of a wealthy man, and her best friend, Ichcha, who comes from a humble background as the daughter of a maid. Despite society's barriers, their unbreakable bond challenges conventions and stands the test of time.

💔 Love takes center stage when Veer, whose marriage proposal was rejected by Tapasya, finds solace in the companionship of Ichcha. But what ensues is a whirlwind of emotions as jealousy and heartbreak threaten to tear apart the inseparable duo.

💍 Witness a gripping twist when Tapasya, fueled by spite, takes a drastic step and marries Veer, setting off a chain of events that creates a complex love triangle. Veer finds himself torn between the two friends, entangled in a web of emotions.

🔄 Spanning over thousands of episodes, 'Uttaran' takes you on an emotional roller-coaster, exploring the lives of these characters, their triumphs, their struggles, and the undeniable fate that intertwines their destinies.

snippet.title: कुष्मांडा माता की आरती | Navratri 2023 Day 4: Kushmanda Mata Aarti | नवरात्रि चौथे दिन की आरती
snippet.description:
कुष्मांडा माता की आरती | Navratri 2023 Day 4: Kushmanda Mata Aarti | नवरात्रि चौथे दिन की आरती

On the fourth day of Navratri 2023, devotees worship Kushmanda Mata, and sing her aarti. Kushmanda Mata is believed to bless her devotees with good health, success, and prosperity. The aarti glorifies her strength and divinity, and seeks her blessings for happiness and peace. Devotees perform puja and offer flowers, fruits, and sweets to the deity. The festive mood resonates in the air as people come together to celebrate the auspicious occasion.

Song - Aarti Kushmanda Maa Ki
Language - Hindi
Album - Soulful Mantras Bhajans Vol 4
Artist - leena bose & aditya jayant ankam
Music Composers - Sourabh Kumar

On our "Spiritual Mantra" channel you will find your beloved deities favorite Bhajan, Mantras, Aarti, Jaap, Chant, Shloka, Amritwani, Kirtan, Pravchan and LIVE darshan etc. 

You can enjoy variour popular bhajan like Shree Krishna Bhajan, Hanuman ji Bhajan, Ganesh ji Bhajan, Shri Ram Bhajan, Shri Laxmi Mata ke Bhajan, Santoshi Maa ke Bhajan, Sherawali Mata ke Bhajan, Shiv Shankar Bhajan, Vishnu Bhajan, Balaji Bhajan, Saibaba Bhajan, Devi Maa ke Bhajan etc. 

Listen to very popular and famous aartiyan like; Aarti Kunj Bihari Ki, Aarti Shri Ramayan Ji Ki, Aarti Kije Hanuman Lala Ki, Sri Gayatri Mata ki Aarti, Om Jai Lakshmi Mata, Om Jai Jagdish Hare, Aarti Sai Baba, Jai Ganesh Deva, Jai Lakshmi Mata, Om Jai Ambe Gauri, Om Jai Shiv Omkara, Aarti Hanuman Ji Ki, Jai Santoshi Mata, Om Jai Shri Shani Deva, Jai Ganesh Deva, Om Jai Shiv Omkara, Ambe Tu Hai Jagdambe etc. 

Also you can enjoy chalisa of your beloved deities like Hanuman Chalisa, Brahma Chalisa, Saraswati Chalisa, Vaishno Devi Chalisa, Krishna Chalisa, Ganesh Chalisa, Durga Chalisa,  Sarasvati Chalisa, Laxmi Chalisa, Shree Ram Chalisa,  Shiv Chalisa, Durga Chalisa, Santoshi Maa Chalisa etc.

Find very popular mantras like Mahamrityunjay Mantra, Gayatri Mantra, Ganesh Mantra, Morning Mantra, Laxmi Mantra, Shiv Mantra, Shani Mantra, Vishnu Sahasranamam Mantra, Shree Siddhivinayak Mantra, Hanuman Mantra, bhajan like Yashomati Maiya Se Bole Nandlala sung by Lata Mangeshkar and other very known singers like Anuradha Paudwal, Kavita Paudwal, Suresh Wadkar, Anup Jalota, Sadhana Sargam, Bela Shende, Shankar Mahadevan, Narendra Chanchal, Richa Sharma, Asha Bhosle, Usha Mangeshkar etc.

🎵 Aarti Saprem ► https://youtu.be/jplKVzyzRcs

🎵 Aarti Kunj Bihari Ki ► https://youtu.be/9Hy3iOHSkTw
🎵 Hanuman Aarti ► https://youtu.be/IUPey3fTpDQ
🎵 Ambe Maa Aarti ► https://youtu.be/SiWHVGUlgsg
🎵 Santoshi Mata Ji Ki Aarti ► https://youtu.be/kXKkRNkMh7U
🎵 Om Jai Laxmi Mata ► https://youtu.be/3eNdpGy05bs

On the fourth day of Navratri 2023, devotees worship Kushmanda Mata, and sing her aarti. Kushmanda Mata is believed to bless her devotees with good health, success, and prosperity. The aarti glorifies her strength and divinity, and seeks her blessings for happiness and peace. Devotees perform puja and offer flowers, fruits, and sweets to the deity. The festive mood resonates in the air as people come together to celebrate the auspicious occasion.

Language - Hindi

snippet.description:
Click here to Subscribe to LIV Comedy:

Jethalal tells his friends that the wine they had consumed is poisonous. A few ambulances enter Gokuldham society. Daya tells Jethalal and his friends that they need not go to hospital.

Show Name - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast - Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt
Episode - 2092
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi, Neela Asit Modi

#taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah #livcomedy #tmkoc #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #comedy #comedy2023 #jethalal #jethalal #jethalalcomedy 

About The Show:
----------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a comedy show inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada Family which consists of uneducated businessmen Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal’s Wife Daya & their naughty Son Tipendra Gada living in 'Gokuldham Co-operative Society' and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. In case of a problem and emergency, Jethalal Gada often rushes to Taarak Mehta to seek his help and guidance as he finds a philosopher in him. The housing society residents help each other find solutions when facing common, real-life challenges and getting involved in sticky situations.

Click here to watch all the fun episodes of Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLSXTaG1fT0cQ9dvdxUiv8H-G_n6fB8VhK

snippet.title: The Mona Lisa Mystery | Why is it World's Most Famous Painting? | Dhruv Rathee
snippet.description:
Compare & Book Fixed Deposits with Stable Money, Download app : https://stablemoney.app.link/gUbgNjY2DDb

In this video, Dhruv Rathee dives deep into the captivating tale of the Mona Lisa. Set in the bustling city of Paris, an audacious theft occurs at the Louvre Museum. The mastermind, Vincenzo Peruggia, along with accomplices Michele Lancelotti and Vincenzo, manage to steal Leonardo da Vinci's iconic painting, the Mona Lisa. Astonishingly, the theft has remained unnoticed for nearly 30 hours. Eventually, the world is alerted to the crime, and even the legendary artist Pablo Picasso is questioned! The painting remains missing for 16 months, and its return to the Louvre only adds to its global fame. We then delve into the woman's identity depicted in the painting, Lisa Gherardini, and the various theories surrounding her. The painting's artistic traits, the science behind Mona Lisa's elusive smile, and the discovery of another possible version of the painting are also discussed. Join us as we unravel the mysteries behind one of the world's most celebrated artworks and its intriguing history.

Link to the video mentioned - 
French Revolution | Why it happened? | The Dark Reality | Dhruv Rathee - https://youtu.be/pGzmmjDDHJg?si=w3XawMcx_LpBUsXc
Mystery of Kohinoor | Curse of World's Most Famous Diamond | Dhruv Rathee - https://youtu.be/ji1fQRWJqlc?si=AnXx6wni3EtU2yua

en.title: The Mona Lisa Mystery | Why is it World's Most Famous Painting? | Dhruv Rathee
en.description:
Compare & Book Fixed Deposits with Stable Money, Download app : https://stablemoney.app.link/gUbgNjY2DDb

In this video, Dhruv Rathee dives deep into the captivating tale of the Mona Lisa. Set in the bustling city of Paris, an audacious theft occurs at the Louvre Museum. The mastermind, Vincenzo Peruggia, along with accomplices Michele Lancelotti and Vincenzo, manage to steal Leonardo da Vinci's iconic painting, the Mona Lisa. Astonishingly, the theft has remained unnoticed for nearly 30 hours. Eventually, the world is alerted to the crime, and even the legendary artist Pablo Picasso is questioned! The painting remains missing for 16 months, and its return to the Louvre only adds to its global fame. We then delve into the woman's identity depicted in the painting, Lisa Gherardini, and the various theories surrounding her. The painting's artistic traits, the science behind Mona Lisa's elusive smile, and the discovery of another possible version of the painting are also discussed. Join us as we unravel the mysteries behind one of the world's most celebrated artworks and its intriguing history.
